title: Brownie Cupcakes with Peanut Butter.
directions: First, stack two oreos with peanut butter, in the middle and on the top and continue with the rest.
Place the oreos in a cupcake liner then in a muffin tin.
Prepare the brownie mix according to the package directions then pour over the cookie stack.
Preheat the oven to 350Â° and bake for 20 minutes.
Let cool before serving and Voila!
